    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep, mirror-like finish and absolutely no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin is pristine, featuring leather that remains supple and a scent that still feels new, with all electronic components and features functioning perfectly. Meticulously maintained with a complete service history, this car offers a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a vehicle in showroom-quality condition without any compromises.",
